---
description: Rails 8 conventions for the sample todo app
alwaysApply: true
---

- Prefer Turbo Streams over custom JavaScript for dynamic responses
- Keep all migrations reversible (use reversible block or up/down methods)
- Always use strong parameters in controllers
- Use `bin/rails generate` rather than hand-writing boilerplate
- Keep schema scoped to the todo app; do not import models or migrations from other projects
- Controllers should respond to HTML and Turbo Streams only
- Shared view partials go in `app/views/shared/`